Additional Privacy Terms:

This software is designed with privacy as a core principle. Users retain full
ownership and control of their location data and personal information. The
software is designed to operate locally without requiring external services
or data transmission, except for optional features that users explicitly
enable with full informed consent.

Map Data Attribution:
This software uses map data from OpenStreetMap contributors, which is available
under the Open Database License (ODbL). Map imagery and data are the property
of their respective providers and are subject to their terms of service.

Contributors agree to maintain the privacy-first principles of this project
and ensure that any contributions do not compromise user privacy or data
ownership rights.
